reviewText: great fireworks with sounds and full program brings me back when was at Disneyland

This was for a friend that wasn't gonna be able to see the fireworks show this year, so she got to still see them at home.  It was received as a thoughtful present and greatly appreciated.  I didn't watch it myself but she said it was perfect.

This video allowed me to relive very special memories from my many trips to Disneyland.  And since I won't be able to go back any time soon, I can just pop in this DVD and have a piece of Disneyland right in my front room.  I love how along with the audio of the fireworks you get the live audio of the guests in the park as they clap and cheer during the shows.
